{"lastModified":1771339469782,"uri":"c::19026008332::vessel::26e91090-ccfb-11ee-a40a-8d6f519b322e","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: San Diego, California, United States\n\nZolna Yachts understands that every opportunity to get together with friends, family or colleagues is unique and special, as should be the chosen venue for your event. Come experience the pinnacle of luxury aboard San Diego’s own Nerissa motor yacht. Let us spoil you and your guests for the time of your lives.\n\nNerissa is a 73 ft Motor Yacht, USCG certified to carry 49 people. The total of 49 people excludes crew but does count all guests and service personnel such as caterers, photographers, etc in the total count of 49 passengers. The design is contemporary with extraordinary design details including custom walnut woodwork throughout, a lighted quartzite bar, stunning furnishings, a professional sound system, multiple outdoor sundecks plus a sparkling hot tub! Services for all types of events are available from small intimate groups to larger corporate gatherings. We have a choice of several fine San Diego caterers. Have one of our on-board chef’s creating delicious passed Hors D’oeuvres with placed platters throughout or whatever your heart desires within your own budget. We provide a fully stocked bar with a bartender included, as well as a top notch professional crew. Two levels of open bar service are available for well or premium beer, wine & spirits. We also offer a cash or tab tab if that suits your group best.","blueprint":{"name":"NERISSA","images":["/media/media::image::c::19026008332::vessel::26e91090-ccfb-11ee-a40a-8d6f519b322e::assets::9a3bda30-ccfd-11ee-a40a-8d6f519b322e.png/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19026008332::vessel::26e91090-ccfb-11ee-a40a-8d6f519b322e::assets::0603b5d0-ccfe-11ee-a40a-8d6f519b322e.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19026008332::vessel::26e91090-ccfb-11ee-a40a-8d6f519b322e::assets::060403f0-ccfe-11ee-a40a-8d6f519b